name: Amazon Mask
description: @DolCreative - During covid-lockdown, like many of us, I experienced some guilt upon realising the increase in my carbon footprint from an increase in Amazon Prime orders. In order to make better use of some of the excess materials I incorporated them into my creative practises. In this case I used the packaging to make a mask, inspired by "Amazon" and some of the Greek mythological/tribal ideas it provoked.
